30 Years of The Blue Bomber: The Evolution of Mega Man|http://www.ign.com/nintendo|https://www.ign.com/videos/2018/09/06/30-years-of-the-blue-bomber-the-evolution-of-mega-man-true-blue-hero||2018-09-06|||30 Years of The Blue Bomber: The Evolution of Mega Man - TRUE BLUE HERO

In this 2nd episode of TRUE BLUE HERO, IGN's own Daemon Hatfield went to Osaka, Japan to talk to the team behind Mega Man 11 about their perspective on working with one of gaming's most iconic franchises and recognizable characters.
